{"content": "I'll solve this step-by-step, converting to base 10, multiplying, then converting back to base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n860\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 6\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 6\u00d79 + 0\u00d71 = 648 + 54 + 0 = 702\u2081\u2080\n\n846\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 6\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 6\u00d71 = 648 + 36 + 6 = 690\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n702 \u00d7 690 = 702 \u00d7 (700 - 10) = 491,400 - 7,020 = 484,380\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n484380 \u00f7 9 = 53820 r 0\n53820 \u00f7 9 = 5980 r 0\n5980 \u00f7 9 = 664 r 4\n664 \u00f7 9 = 73 r 7\n73 \u00f7 9 = 8 r 1\n8 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 8\n\nReading from bottom to top: 817400\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n817400\u2089 = 8\u00d759049 + 1\u00d76561 + 7\u00d7729 + 4\u00d781 + 0\u00d79 + 0\u00d71\n= 472392 + 6561 + 5103 + 324 + 0 + 0 = 484,380\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n817400", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 453}